I was wondering about this as well.

Looks like the build for nightly Mac GPU Python 3 is currently broken, and for this reason link to the last successful build of nightly Mac GPU Python 3 version 1.1.0 is broken. Same issue with nightly Mac GPU Python 2 1.1.0 link and build.
